@startuml
!theme plain
title The Iterative Evaluation Loop

state "Wave 0: Safety Check" as W0
state "Wave 1: Seed Test (500)" as W1
state "Wave 2: Niche Test (5k)" as W2
state "Wave 3: Broad Test (100k+)" as W3
state "Inventory (Search)" as Inv

[*] --> W0
W0 --> W1 : Safe
W0 --> [*] : Copyright/Spam

W1 --> W2 : VVSA > 60%
W1 --> Inv : Failed

W2 --> W3 : APV > 85%
W2 --> Inv : Failed (The 5k Plateau)

W3 --> W3 : Metrics Stable (Viral)
W3 --> Inv : Saturation
@enduml